  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Open the filo pastry package and cut it into 12 equal squares.",
    "Mix the ricotta cheese, chopped parsley, black pepper, salt, and lemon juice in a bowl.",
    "Place an ancho chilli in the center of each filo square and brush the edges with olive oil.",
    "Place a tablespoon of ricotta mixture on top of the chilli and fold the pastry over to form a triangle.",
    "Bake for 20 minutes or until the pastry is golden brown.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy!"
  ],
